 initialize properly. However, previous tests might have already initialized it. I realize that running isolated tests would be a safer approach overall to prevent any unexpected behavior. Let's keep testing in mind as I proceed!\n\n**Finalizing test class rules**\n\nI'm sorting through the guidelines for class names and file names for reader tests. The rule states that only top-level public classes should be used in naming, which means inner helper classes aren't allowed. I questioned whether the file name is okay, so I'm confirming it. I think I've got to finalize my approach to this, making sure it meets all requirements!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0eb74b9aad09859f016a246010ac388190a0a37293ce23ebea\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJGAtGXq_kD8vG_VUliSWFL3ykhI2Yv-BFiu_oUnJTLW60flGAI_AqXdbLCsY95JsfzjcRwuqHhbYHF9hP4Y9KFKAYM6POFbnIRzQyL0O0w9yf8m4D7l-PX_d2QYJODHlIQD1bsqAiwX93DnBl_c6pW79g-icrYNwR7y8CBZF0pkOdVWH99j6ST2sDRC_yS8tJEZpntOGUqIS08GWHG4bSZ8FK0gXeOB1cbUqTS5mTR-lrvn-T0zvRvR0eLQYKV1-ZhbBEBw6efi549cVyTkDCheDHOhFBUNR7BfqJH0xV7Q91HcRjXdAPPoxB3HXo1NecplhDePq-SKx-3OlB3XPCRUrOjyxL62wkiOaS7tmb6Ptu8Bb-UmpJ3xoxJd6pFzSmoGbwYDB5tQIQbtc1cfTSdTZfr4gCB7ZnUyOqnn7wo0Zvr1jcMCN1IWJ9aNMWALXjjyPifBZ9G3tQ02RNdVMMVcq3ubrANh3jXPxUoLafwzwaX9wrfCgUJA9SManaMVcC-j1PT2wizM0YbrsaDwuKXKHX0L3qL_a3uimVVGQ0cXOzr5h9cS8EbYLFVN561jXBixEgfeWCCBNyVTHJ-XYY5rfQjcpPtHEkG3mYrncojq9y0sxFZK6yAGI_V_yqmhYuufgMxLXrGxb5oFdDxEiNRNxY4Yg8AVeN61rAH5qG2G88zwDnv8ZC-Evg78a9Gtz3NcHXBVNFsstFBfsb-p6w6KKBG-wOD-B1UbXlvmLcfMpxvbArGWXg9KV9aRigYbnHvVE3XerDI8mNKhFncXMldUEg98ifveM8gGy9rKjMFiLCBkgaywEsWCX6dZEbvSVKPmLGs_sN166meQBvdfj4WHLB696sXna7qKjgYFrLGMyIEj1uj04Y2NDFmzeFF1c_0CA2vGesxDyaonW48ckMjuqxY2cIZ4AhbIc9SBnnnDxBnrG917BvqF5f_IJBvIo7y3ngz5cGUPQMv7ZwdOHLK11n0iSDh7Tq51LhIQSi4t8aK2ghK9kl8cTZvzbb5WSJ6hSxwye1s7JxhP2hyZeTDIGtdrU51JwU33fvAsLkmd61zhHeCM-obt8MCbHe52a3vJuzN5kXUcAA1rCchHfydKPjaaXAvJ8JPotUkcxGZEp6mtrDOAv46MuG5u8ehCAV1V6H18ustGLPYNXGz7qZ2GTFXIjOfGQgDeb3WDj7h-EqcRsYl6oV7U